00001 /******************************************************************************
00002 * File      : intDE_tria3.c                                                   *
00003 * Author    : Carlos Rosales Fernandez (carlos@ihpc.a-star.edu.sg)            *
00004 * Date      : 01-09-2006                                                      *
00005 * Revision  : 1.0                                                             *
00006 *******************************************************************************
00007 * DESCRIPTION                                                                 *
00008 * Computes the integral of the 2nd, 3rd and 4th order derivatives of the 3D   *
00009 * Green's function for one element and returns the integrals in matrix        *
00010 * E[][][][] for the 3 dimensions and each node.                               *
00011 * Works for linear interpolation in triangular elements (3-noded triangles).  *
00012 * These are some examples:                                                    *
00013 *                                                                             *
00014 * Efield[0][1][0][0] = Ex @ node 1                                            *
00015 * Efield[0][0][1][0] = Ey @ node 1                                            *
00016 * Efield[0][2][0][0] = dEx/dx @ node 1                                        *
00017 * Efield[0][1][0][1] = dEx/dz = dEz/dx @ node 1                               *
00018 * Efield[2][0][1][3] = d3Ez/dydz2 = d3Ey/dz3 @ node 3                         *
00019 *                                                                             *
00020 * Where Ex = dG/dx, Ey = dG/dy and Ez = dG/dz and G is Green's function.      *
00021 ******************************************************************************/

00048 int intDE_tria3(unsigned int nOrder, double X[3][3], double *Xeval, 
00049                 double Efield[][7][7][7])
00050 {
00051     const unsigned int NODES_IN_ELEM = 3;
00052     unsigned int i, j, k, m;
00053     double A, B, C, D, E, F, dx, dx2, dx4, dy, dy2, dy4, dz, dz2, dz4, J, rsq, W;
00054     double DE[80], L[2], N[3], XL[3];
00055 
00056     /* Initialize */
00057     for(i = 0; i < NODES_IN_ELEM; i++)
00058         for(j = 0; j < 7; j++)
00059             for(k = 0; k < 7; k++)
00060                 for(m = 0; m < 7; m++) Efield[i][j][k][m] = 0.0;
00061 
00062     /* Integrate using Gauss-Legendre quadrature */
00063     for(i = 0; i < TNGAUSS; i++){
00064         L[0] = TGauss[i][0];
00065         L[1] = TGauss[i][1];
00066         W = TGauss[i][2];
00067 
00068         /* Shape functions N and Jacobian J for these (L1,L2) values */
00069         shape_tria3(L,N);       
00070         J = X2L_tria3(X,XL,L,N);
00071 
00072         /* Auxiliar quantities */
00073         dx = Xeval[0] - XL[0];
00074         dy = Xeval[1] - XL[1];
00075         dz = Xeval[2] - XL[2];
00076         dx2 = dx*dx;
00077         dy2 = dy*dy;
00078         dz2 = dz*dz;
00079         rsq = dx2 + dy2 + dz2;
00080         A = J*W/pow(rsq,1.5);
00081         B = 3.0*A/rsq;
00082 
00083         /***********************************************/
00084         /*** GET CONTRIBUTION FROM EACH ELEMENT NODE ***/
00085         /***********************************************/
00086     
00087         /* First order derivatives of the electric field */
00088         DE[0] = A - B*dx2;  /* dEx/dx */
00089         DE[1] = -B*dx*dy;   /* dEx/dy */
00090         DE[2] = -B*dx*dz;   /* dEx/dz */
00091     
00092         DE[3] = A - B*dy2;  /* dEy/dy */
00093         DE[4] = -B*dy*dz;   /* dEy/dz */
00094 
00095         DE[5] = A - B*dz2;  /* dEz/dz */
00096     
00097         /* Second order derivatives of the electric field */
00098         if(nOrder > 1){
00099             C = 5.0*B/rsq;
00100 
00101             DE[6] = (C*dx2 - 3.0*B)*dx;     /* d2Ex/dx2  */
00102             DE[7] = (C*dx2 - B)*dy;         /* d2Ex/dxdy */
00103             DE[8] = (C*dx2 - B)*dz;         /* d2Ex/dxdz */
00104             DE[9] = (C*dy2 - B)*dx;         /* d2Ex/dy2  */
00105             DE[10] = C*dx*dy*dz;            /* d2Ex/dydz */
00106             DE[11] = (C*dz2 - B)*dx;        /* d2Ex/dzdz */
00107         
00108             DE[12] = (C*dy2 - 3.0*B)*dy;    /* d2Ey/dy2  */
00109             DE[13] = (C*dy2 - B)*dz;        /* d2Ey/dydz */
00110             DE[14] = (C*dz2 - B)*dy;        /* d2Ey/dz2  */
00111         
00112             DE[15] = (C*dz2 - 3.0*B)*dz;    /* d2Ez/dz2  */
00113         
00114             /* Third order derivatives of the electric field */
00115             if(nOrder > 2){
00116                 D = 7.0*C/rsq;
00117             
00118                 DE[16] = (-D*dx2 + 6.0*C)*dx2 - 3.0*B;      /* d3Ex/dx3    */
00119                 DE[17] = (-D*dx2 + 3.0*C)*dx*dy;            /* d3Ex/dx2dy  */
00120                 DE[18] = (-D*dx2 + 3.0*C)*dx*dz;            /* d3Ex/dx2dz  */
00121                 DE[19] = -D*dx2*dy2 + C*(dx2 + dy2) - B;    /* d3Ex/dxdy2  */
00122                 DE[20] = (-D*dx2 + C)*dy*dz;                /* d3Ex/dxdydz */
00123                 DE[21] = -D*dx2*dz2 + C*(dx2 + dz2) - B;    /* d3Ex/dxdz2  */
00124                 DE[22] = (-D*dy2 + 3.0*C)*dx*dy;            /* d3Ex/dy3    */
00125                 DE[23] = (-D*dy2 + C)*dx*dz;                /* d3Ex/dy2dz  */
00126                 DE[24] = (-D*dz2 + C)*dx*dy;                /* d3Ex/dydz2  */
00127                 DE[25] = (-D*dz2 + 3.0*C)*dx*dz;            /* d3Ex/dz3    */
00128         
00129                 DE[26] = (-D*dy2 + 6.0*C)*dy2 - 3.0*B;      /* d3Ey/dy3    */
00130                 DE[27] = (-D*dy2 + 3.0*C)*dy*dz;            /* d3Ey/dy2dz  */
00131                 DE[28] = -D*dy2*dz2 + C*(dy2 + dz2) - B;    /* d3Ey/dydz2  */
00132                 DE[29] = (-D*dz2 + 3.0*C)*dy*dz;            /* d3Ey/dz3    */
00133         
00134                 DE[30] = (-D*dz2 + 6.0*C)*dz2 - 3.0*B;      /* d3Ez/dz3    */
00135             
00136                 /* Fourth order derivatives of the electric field */
00137                 if(nOrder > 3){
00138                     E=9.0*D/rsq;
00139 
00140                     dx4 = dx2*dx2;
00141                     dy4 = dy2*dy2;
00142                     dz4 = dz2*dz2;
00143     
00144                     DE[31] = (E*dx4 - 10.0*D*dx2 + 15.0*C)*dx;              /* d4Ex/dx4     */
00145                     DE[32] = (E*dx4 - 6.0*D*dx2 + 3.0*C)*dy;                /* d4Ex/dx3dy   */
00146                     DE[33] = (E*dx4 - 6.0*D*dx2 + 3.0*C)*dz;                /* d4Ex/dx3dz   */
00147                     DE[34] = (E*dx2*dy2-D*(dx2 + 3.0*dy2) + 3.0*C)*dx;      /* d4Ex/dx2dy2  */
00148                     DE[35] = (E*dx2 - 3.0*D)*dx*dy*dz;                      /* d4Ex/dx2dydz */
00149                     DE[36] = (E*dx2*dz2 - D*(dx2 + 3.0*dz2) + 3.0*C)*dx;    /* d4Ex/dx2dz2  */
00150                     DE[37] = (E*dx2*dy2 - D*(dy2 + 3.0*dx2) + 3.0*C)*dy;    /* d4Ex/dxdy3   */
00151                     DE[38] = (E*dx2*dy2 - D*(dx2 + dy2) + C)*dz;            /* d4Ex/dxdy2dz */
00152                     DE[39] = (E*dx2*dz2 - D*(dx2 + dz2) + C)*dy;            /* d4Ex/dxdydz2 */
00153                     DE[40] = (E*dx2*dz2 - D*(dz2 + 3.0*dx2) + 3.0*C)*dz;    /* d4Ex/dxdz3   */
00154                     DE[41] = (E*dy4 - 6.0*D*dy2 + 3.0*C)*dx;                /* d4Ex/dy4     */
00155                     DE[42] = (E*dy2 - 3.0*D)*dx*dy*dz;                      /* d4Ex/dy3dz   */
00156                     DE[43] = (E*dy2*dz2 - D*(dy2 + dz2) + C)*dx;            /* d4Ex/dy2dz2  */
00157                     DE[44] = (E*dz2 - 3.0*D)*dx*dy*dz;                      /* d4Ex/dydz3   */
00158                     DE[45] = (E*dz4 - 6.0*D*dz2 + 3.0*C)*dx;                /* d4E/dz4      */
00159                 
00160                     DE[46] = (E*dy4 - 10.0*D*dy2 + 15.0*C)*dy;              /* d4Ey/dy4     */
00161                     DE[47] = (E*dy4 - 6.0*D*dy2 + 3.0*C)*dz;                /* d4Ey/dy3dz   */
00162                     DE[48] = (E*dy2*dz2 - D*(dy2 + 3.0*dz2) + 3.0*C)*dy;    /* d4Ey/dy2dz2  */
00163                     DE[49] = (E*dy2*dz2 - D*(dz2 + 3.0*dy2) + 3.0*C)*dz;    /* d4Ey/dydz3   */
00164                     DE[50] = (E*dz4 - 6.0*D*dz2 + 3.0*C)*dy;                /* d4Ey/dz4     */
00165                 
00166                     DE[51] = (E*dz4 - 10.0*D*dz2 + 15.0*C)*dz;              /* d4Ez/dz4     */
00167                 
00168                     /* Fifth order derivatives of the electric field */
00169                     if(nOrder > 4){
00170                         F = 11.0*E/rsq;
00171                 
00172                         DE[52] = -F*dx4*dx2 + 15.0*E*dx4 - 45.0*D*dx2 + 15.0*C;                         /* d5Ex/dx5      */
00173                         DE[53] = (-F*dx4 + 10.0*E*dx2 - 15.0*D)*dx*dy;                                  /* d5Ex/dx4dy    */
00174                         DE[54] = (-F*dx4 + 10.0*E*dx2 - 15.0*D)*dx*dz;                                  /* d5Ex/dx4dz    */
00175                         DE[55] = -F*dx4*dy2 + E*(dx4 + 6.0*dx2*dy2) - D*(3.0*dy2 + 6.0*dx2) + 3.0*C;    /* d5Ex/dx3dy2   */
00176                         DE[56] = (-F*dx4 + 6.0*E*dx2 - 3.0*D)*dy*dz;                                    /* d5Ex/dx3dydz  */
00177                         DE[57] = -F*dx4*dz2 + E*(dx4 + 6.0*dx2*dz2) - D*(3.0*dz2 + 6.0*dx2) + 3.0*C;    /* d5Ex/dx3dz2   */
00178                         DE[58] = (-F*dx2*dy2 + 3.0*E*(dx2 + dy2) - 9.0*D)*dx*dy;                        /* d5Ex/dx2dy3   */
00179                         DE[59] = (-F*dx2*dy2 + E*(dx2 + 3.0*dy2) - 3.0*D)*dx*dz;                        /* d5Ex/dx2dy2dz */
00180                         DE[60] = (-F*dx2*dz2 + E*(dx2 + 3.0*dz2) - 3.0*D)*dx*dy;                        /* d5Ex/dx2dydz2 */
00181                         DE[61] = (-F*dx2*dz2 + 3.0*E*(dx2 + dz2) - 9.0*D)*dx*dz;                        /* d5Ex/dx2dz3   */
00182                         DE[62] = -F*dx2*dy4 + E*(dy4 + 6.0*dy2*dx2) - D*(3.0*dx2 + 6.0*dy2) + 3.0*C;    /* d5Ex/dxdy4    */
00183                         DE[63] = (-F*dx2*dy2 + E*(dy2 + 3.0*dx2) - 3.0*D)*dy*dz;                        /* d5Ex/dxdy3dz  */
00184                         DE[64] = -F*dx2*dy2*dz2 + E*(dx2*dy2 + dx2*dz2 + dy2*dz2) - D*rsq + C;          /* d5Ex/dxdy2dz2 */
00185                         DE[65] = (-F*dx2*dz2 + E*(dz2 + 3.0*dx2) - 3.0*D)*dy*dz;                        /* d5Ex/dxdydz3  */
00186                         DE[66] = -F*dx2*dz4 + E*(dz4 + 6.0*dx2*dz2) - D*(3.0*dx2 + 6.0*dz2) + 3.0*C;    /* d5Ex/dxdz4    */
00187                         DE[67] = (-F*dy4 + 10.0*E*dy2 - 15.0*D)*dx*dy;                                  /* d5Ex/dy5      */
00188                         DE[68] = (-F*dy4 + 6.0*E*dy2 - 3.0*D)*dx*dz;                                    /* d5Ex/dy4dz    */
00189                         DE[69] = (-F*dy2*dz2 + E*(dy2 + 3.0*dz2) - 3.0*D)*dx*dy;                        /* d5Ex/dy3dz2   */
00190                         DE[70] = (-F*dy2*dz2 + E*(dz2 + 3.0*dy2) - 3.0*D)*dx*dz;                        /* d5Ex/dy2dz3   */
00191                         DE[71] = (-F*dz4 + 6.0*E*dz2 - 3.0*D)*dx*dy;                                    /* d5Ex/dydz4    */
00192                         DE[72] = (-F*dz4 + 10.0*E*dz2 - 15.0*D)*dx*dz;                                  /* d5Ex/dz5      */
00193     
00194                         DE[73] = -F*dy4*dy2 + 15.0*E*dy4 - 45.0*D*dy2 + 15.0*C;                         /* d5Ey/dy5      */
00195                         DE[74] = (-F*dy4 + 10.0*E*dy2 - 15.0*D)*dy*dz;                                  /* d5Ey/dy4dz    */
00196                         DE[75] = -F*dy4*dz2 + E*(dy4 + 6.0*dz2*dy2) - D*(3.0*dz2 + 6.0*dy2) + 3.0*C;    /* d5Ey/dy3dz2   */
00197                         DE[76] = (-F*dy2*dz2 + 3.0*E*(dy2 + dz2) - 9.0*D)*dy*dz;                        /* d5Ey/dy2dz3   */
00198                         DE[77] = -F*dy2*dz4 + E*(dz4 + 6.0*dy2*dz2) - D*(3.0*dy2 + 6.0*dz2) + 3.0*C;    /* d5Ey/dydz4    */
00199                         DE[78] = (-F*dz4 + 10.0*E*dz2 - 15.0*D)*dy*dz;                                  /* d5Ey/dz5      */
00200                     
00201                         DE[79] = -F*dz4*dz2 + 15.0*E*dz4 - 45.0*D*dz2 + 15.0*C;                         /* d5Ez/dz5      */
00202                     }
00203                 }
00204             }
00205         }
00206     
00207         /* Add contributions from all nodes */
00208         for(j = 0; j < NODES_IN_ELEM; j++){
00209             Efield[j][2][0][0] += DE[0]*N[j];
00210             Efield[j][1][1][0] += DE[1]*N[j];
00211             Efield[j][1][0][1] += DE[2]*N[j];
00212             Efield[j][0][2][0] += DE[3]*N[j];
00213             Efield[j][0][1][1] += DE[4]*N[j];

00215             
00216             if(nOrder > 1){
00217                 Efield[j][3][0][0] += DE[6]*N[j];
00218                 Efield[j][2][1][0] += DE[7]*N[j];
00219                 Efield[j][2][0][1] += DE[8]*N[j];
